data.description: LOCATION LOCATION LOCATION! Spacious 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with 2 car garage & enough parking for 5 vehicles. Large front deck on second level as well as covered back deck provide additional outdoor space to enjoy the brilliant sunrises & beautiful sunsets. There is even a space that offers a partial water view. Home features high ceilings, open floor plan, laundry room, storage space & more! Home has upside potential and a great opportunity to customize to your specifications. New roof 8 years, A/C 5 years, water heater less than 2 years old. Close to restaurants, boutiques, mini golf, parks, public transportation, grocery stores & more. This is a great location adjacent to the sugar sand beach with a lighted crosswalk right out the front door. A perfect spot to enjoy beach life and all that the Gulf of Mexico has to offer.
